<plot>A local news man/celebrity and his crew are on the mission of saving a once prosperous and now abandoned village from being demolished by a greedy resort developers. While shooting a segment about the history of the village they encounter local settlers from a nearby village who know nothing of the upcoming doom of their surroundings. Sensing an even bigger story, the newsman and his crew let themselves be invited to the feast in their honor. Little do they know that this is to be their last supper...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?057501</url></doc>
